summary: CONTINUAL GLARE FROM SUV AND SPORTS OR PSEUDO SPORTS VEHICLES WITH HIGH HEADLIGHTS, GLARING FOG LIGHTS, OR FOUR SETS OF LIGHTS THAT ARE TURNED ON AND APPROXIMATE THE HIGH BEAMS OF MOST OTHER CARS. THIS GLARE IS AT TIMES VERY DANGEROUS AND MAKES FOR VERY POOR VISIBILITY AND A HIGH POSSIBILITY OF WRECKS ESPECIALLY DURING BAD WET OR SNOWY WEATHER.   *NLM
